{"tid":1965122,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"大家係手足既話請unfollow Lucy 李元元 ig","createTime":"2020-04-09T09:21:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T03:29:05.000Z","uid":220066,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"1543245861515d2435c591c967b365b5e4517755","tid":1965122,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T09:21:35.000Z","msg":"首先我見好多手足都有Follow Lucy ig<br />\n知道呢個小朋友好得意好受歡迎<br />\n但係唔好唔記得佢老母係扮曬中立<br />\n又要扮撚曬和平使者，其實咪又係藍絲一名<br />\n係運動入面指指點點係度話人唔岩<br />\n好心你啦唔知頭唔知路就唔好亂up野啦<br />\n你有無見到好多無辜既人被黑警打到仆街呀<br />\n呢樣你又知唔知呀？<br />\n<br />\n仲有你平時成撚日要逼個女上鏡應酬<br />\n好難怪你個女會發脾氣架喎<br />\n人地係有話事權唔係話你想擺佢上Ig就Ig<br />\n你有無問過你個女女想唔想被放上ig比人睇<br />\n你根本正一係仆街，為左R讚助<br />\n係咁推個女出去賺錢<br />\n由頭到尾你都係當個女係搖錢樹<br />\n無尊重過Lucy既諗法<br />\n做老母做到你咁真係好仆街囉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/09/172043_5c5b599b065d6b5214a3f694a3a02d86.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2F172043_5c5b599b065d6b5214a3f694a3a02d86.png&h=e1e5ef57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab94d99b21cb61ba038b2b726912db90fdb49c86","tid":1965122,"uid":124180,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T09:23:12.000Z","msg":"唔識 邊個嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d884721854bfb8be4f711cb6f7c38df3a073a2","tid":1965122,"uid":354823,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T09:28:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1aeeb361484225b5b4bfab7b3cb6f35f50e4100","tid":1965122,"uid":220431,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T09:29:11.000Z","msg":"ON9 如果我個女唔開心 我要全世界都一樣唔開心<br />\n當自己個女係小醜咩"},{"pid":"0ac886043c87a9d9d46581c733fdbc03f7570ba4","tid":1965122,"uid":35457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T09:30:01.000Z